Package: videogridplayer
Version: 1.2.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Video Grid Player <noreply@example.com>
Section: video
Priority: optional
Description: Video Grid Player
 A cross-platform desktop application that displays video thumbnails
 in a configurable grid and plays them fullscreen via VLC.
 .
 Features include multi-page navigation, multilingual UI, thumbnail
 customisation, shuffle playback, and video title translation.
